content.text: Good, the `schools` table has a `Phone` column. Now let me find the top 3 schools by excellence rate (NumGE1500 / NumTstTakr) and their phone numbers.

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT s.sname, s.NumGE1500, s.NumTstTakr, CAST(s.NumGE1500 AS REAL) / s.NumTstTakr AS excellence_rate, sc.Phone FROM satscores s JOIN schools sc ON s.cds = sc.CDSCode WHERE s.NumGE1500 IS NOT NULL AND s.NumTstTakr > 0 ORDER BY excellence_rate DESC LIMIT 10;"
